Fri Aug 30 17:09:22 EDT 2002	nsc <Nicholas_Castellano@acml.com>
	* include/sybdb.h:
	- Add prototypes for new functions dbsetlname(), dbsetlbool(),
	  dbsetlshort(), and dbsetllong().  Use these to implement macros
	  for DBSETL*() and BCP_SETL*().
